Terraform stack cloudwatch-log-group-persistent to create below 2 CloudWatch groups with KMS keys
- CW group name: apache-access-log
  retention period: 14
  encrypted with your KMS key

- CW group name: apache-error-log
  retention period: 14
  encrypted with your KMS key


Question:
- Is CloudWatch agent installed on instances able to create CW group automatically?
- If the answer is yes, why we create CW group here? What is the business requrement?

